rule_name: flowers with (purple centers or orange stems) and thorns
text: Hello. Look for the plant with spikes on the stem and the stem is colored in.

rule_name: flowers with (purple centers or orange stems) and thorns

rule_name: flowers with (purple centers or orange stems) and thorns
